@startuml external vendor fault


title Критический сценарий отказа внешней системы бронирования


participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Trip Service" as Service
participant "Circuit Breaker" as CB
database "DB & Cache" as DB
participant "External Vendor API" as Vendor


== Нормальная работа (Happy Path) ==


Gateway -> Service: GET /trips/{id}
activate Service


Service -> CB: call(vendor_id)
activate CB
CB -> Vendor: API Request
activate Vendor
Vendor --[#green]> CB: 200 OK (Fresh Data)
deactivate Vendor
CB --[#green]> Service: Fresh Data
deactivate CB


Service -> DB: Update Stale Cache (JSONB)
Service --> Gateway: 200 OK (Data, IsFresh: true)


== Обработка сбоя (Error Handling / Fallback) ==


Gateway -> Service: GET /trips/{id}
alt Circuit Breaker CLOSED (Первый сбой)
   Service -> CB: call(vendor_id)
   activate CB
   CB -> Vendor: API Request
   activate Vendor
   Vendor --[#red]> CB: Timeout / 5xx Error
   deactivate Vendor
   CB --[#red]> Service: Exception
   deactivate CB
else Circuit Breaker OPEN (Последующие запросы)
   Service -> CB: call(vendor_id)
   activate CB
   CB --[#red]> Service: Fast Fail (Exception)
   deactivate CB
end


Service -> DB: Fetch Last Successful Data
activate DB
DB --> Service: Stale Data + Timestamp
deactivate DB


Service --> Gateway: 200 OK (Stale Data, IsFresh: false)
deactivate Service


@enduml
